OBJECT Report 23044601 DSHIP Pkg. Carrier Label 4x6
{
  OBJECT-PROPERTIES
  {
    Date=03/14/19;
    Time=[ 5:14:26 PM];
    Version List=DSHIP2.2.2;
  }
  PROPERTIES
  {
    CaptionML=[ENU=Dynamic Ship Pkg. Carrier Label 4x6;
               ESM=Etiqueta de soporte Pkg. Dynamic Ship 4 x 6;
               FRC=êtiquette d'Pkg. Carrier Dynamic Ship 4 x 6;
               ENC=Dynamic Ship Pkg. Carrier Label 4x6];
    OnPreReport=VAR
                  lrecDShipSetup@1000000001 : Record 23044600;
                  lrecLabelData@1000000000 : Record 23044622;
                  lcuPackRateMgmt@1000000002 : Codeunit 23044602;
                  lcuScaleMgmt@1000000006 : Codeunit 23044610;
                  loptLabelType@1000000004 : Option;
                  lbAllFound@1000000005 : Boolean;
                  lbPrintResult@1000000003 : Boolean;
                BEGIN
                  // this should disable print from preview
                  IF ( CurrReport.PREVIEW ) THEN
                    EXIT;

                  lrecDShipSetup.GET;
                  CASE lrecDShipSetup."Carrier Label Print Type" OF
                    lrecDShipSetup."Carrier Label Print Type"::Image:
                      EXIT;
                  END;

                  IF ( NOT diLPHeader.FINDSET(FALSE) ) THEN
                    EXIT;


                  lcuScaleMgmt.getLabelType(loptLabelType);

                  REPEAT
                    // "Label Type"::Additional will be contained within the Shipping ZPL
                    lbPrintResult := lbPrintResult OR
                                     lcuPackRateMgmt.printZPLLabel(loptLabelType,
                                                                   diLPHeader."No.");
                  UNTIL((diLPHeader.NEXT()=0) OR NOT lbPrintResult);

                  IF ( lbPrintResult ) THEN
                    CurrReport.QUIT;
                END;

  }
  DATASET
  {
    { 1000000000;;DataItem;diLPHeader        ;
               DataItemTable=Table23044505 }

    { 1000000001;1;DataItem;diLabelData      ;
               DataItemTable=Table23044622;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(Entry No.);
               OnAfterGetRecord=VAR
                                  lcuScaleMgmt@1000000000 : Codeunit 23044610;
                                  loptLabelType@1000000001 : Option;
                                BEGIN
                                  lcuScaleMgmt.getLabelType(loptLabelType);
                                  // these are separated for easier readability/maintainability

                                  // non-png are handled outside of the report and will generate blank pages.
                                  IF (diLabelData."Label Format" <> diLabelData."Label Format"::PNG) THEN
                                    CurrReport.SKIP;

                                  // there may not be label data if an external carrier doesn't fill it.
                                  IF (NOT diLabelData.Label.HASVALUE) THEN
                                    CurrReport.SKIP;

                                  IF ( loptLabelType = diLabelData."Label Type"::Shipping ) THEN BEGIN
                                    IF ( (diLabelData."Label Type" <> loptLabelType) AND
                                         (diLabelData."Label Type" <> diLabelData."Label Type"::Additional) ) THEN
                                      CurrReport.SKIP;
                                  END ELSE BEGIN
                                    IF ( diLabelData."Label Type" <> loptLabelType ) THEN
                                      CurrReport.SKIP;
                                  END;

                                  diLabelData.CALCFIELDS(Label);
                                END;

               DataItemLink=License Plate No.=FIELD(No.) }

    { 1000000003;2;Column;fldLabel           ;
               SourceExpr=diLabelData.Label }

  }
